Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.19,0:18:07.12,IN-CH_EP03,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}两人影交织 随旋律飘摇
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.12,0:18:11.28,IN-CH_EP03,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}直到落入地狱深处
